{"id":9020,"date":"2020-07-24T03:56:50","date_gmt":"2020-07-24T03:56:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=9020"},"modified":"2021-02-27T03:29:23","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T03:29:23","slug":"phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00ccM HI\u1ec2U PHONG C\u00c1CH N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T D\u1eaaN \u0110\u1ea6U XU H\u01af\u1edaNG N\u0102M 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>Phong c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh. N\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng n\u00f3i chung. Hi\u1ec3u theo ngh\u0129a r\u1ed9ng, phong c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho n\u1ec1n v\u0103n minh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i. N\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t ri\u00eang t\u01b0 v\u00e0 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean t\u1eebng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u00ec phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m 2020 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/Byzannoithathiendai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Byzan Interior<\/a> chia s\u1ebb d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\" class=\"wp-image-9021\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/4.2.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u0103m 2020, phong c\u00e1ch Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch b\u1edfi v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eaft l\u1ecdc, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao cho m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i &#8211; Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201ct\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n, tinh t\u1ebf\u201d nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u00ednh c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf trong c\u00e1ch b\u00e0y bi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1ed1i \u0111a. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u1edf phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\" class=\"wp-image-9023\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/5-2.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111a c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng. M\u1ed9t v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh hai kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m k\u1ec7 s\u00e1ch ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i. Hay chi\u1ebfc b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n \u0103n, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc b\u00e0n \u0103n linh ho\u1ea1t.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\" class=\"wp-image-9024\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/1-3.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Nh\u1eefng v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n th\u00f4 c\u1ee9ng, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00ed b\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf; thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, mang t\u00ednh \u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ec7 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u gia ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gian sinh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n, t\u1eebng khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n chia b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/thiet-ke-noi-tha-villa-thai-nguyen-2\/\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Villa Th\u00e1i Nguy\u00ean sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Danh h\u1ecda ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd Leonardo Da Vinci \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng: \u201c\u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng\u201d. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng ho\u00e0n m\u1ef9, t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 trau chu\u1ed1t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf trong ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 s\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c, kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ea1nh l\u1ebdo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n s\u01a1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2-2-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\" class=\"wp-image-9025\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2-2-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2-2-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2-2-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/2-2.jpg 1125w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00e0o, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. B\u1edfi n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1edbi c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, c\u00e1ch b\u00e0y tr\u00ed v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac mang t\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9n b\u1ec1, lo toan c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u g\u1ed7, \u0111\u00e1, kim lo\u1ea1i, k\u00ednh,&#8230;\u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"byzan-thiet-ke-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9026\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/3-2.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-chung-cu-sunshine-city-tay-ho\/\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Sunshine City hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, sang tr\u1ecdng<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u cao c\u1ea5p, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef trong ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u \u0111\u01a1n s\u1eafc lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. B\u1edfi n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng rung c\u1ea3m cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng, m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh \u0111\u01a1n s\u1eafc c\u00f2n gi\u00fap nh\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng gian hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/P-khach-4-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\" class=\"wp-image-9027\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/P-khach-4-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/P-khach-4-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/upload