 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 cho m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a s\u00e0n &#8211; t\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; tr\u1ea7n &#8211; \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 decor trang tr\u00ed. Ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u hay nh\u1ea5n theo v\u00f9ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/17-2-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"byzan-thiet-ke-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9029\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/17-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/17-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/17-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/17-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/17-2.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec7n nghi, t\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn phong c\u00e1ch Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m 2020. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch s\u1ef1 tr\u1ebb trung, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang th\u00ec phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan<\/a> l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, uy t\u00edn trong ng\u00e0nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan ch\u1ec9 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u1ea3ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, Byzan \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi c\u00f4ng chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c trong phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Phong c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh. N\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng n\u00f3i chung. Hi\u1ec3u theo ngh\u0129a r\u1ed9ng, phong c\u00e1ch&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":9026,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[155],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-9020","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong-noi-that"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9020","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/